sql_statement.static: SELECT 'Lost Stream' AS `Failure Category`,'stream '||StreamBlockName||' did not reach RX port'
WHERE EXISTS (SELECT DscpName FROM DscpNWThresholds WHERE StreamBlockName NOT LIKE 'EF%' AND StreamBlockName LIKE DscpName||'%')
AND ParentStreamBlock NOT IN (SELECT ParentStreamBlock FROM RxEotStreamResults WHERE IsExpectedPort=1)
